{
  "total_duration": 681.975,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.256,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Stop thief!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“捉贼！”它不是完整的礼貌句子，而是一声很短、很急的 street cry：有人看到小偷跑走，就可能喊"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Stop thief!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 14.606,
      "end": 25.726,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把安全边界说清楚。这课像一段老式街头动作镜头，但现实生活中，孩子不要追小偷，不要冲进马路，更不要模仿开车拦截别人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 26.076,
      "end": 39.396,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天更现代、更安全的做法是：move to a safe place，remember details，tell an adult or security staff，and call the police。真正处理危险的是 trained adults。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 39.745,
      "end": 52.249,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事里的 Roy Trenton 是一个 adult bus driver。他原来开出租车，后来成了公交车司机，而且"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he has not regretted it"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，因为新工作 far more exciting。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 52.599,
      "end": 62.679,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "有一天，他沿着 Catford Street 开车，看见两个 thieves 从商店里 rush out，朝一辆 waiting car 跑去，其中一个还提着 a bag full of money。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 63.029,
      "end": 77.829,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整课记忆链是：taxi -> bus -> more exciting -> thieves rush out -> bag of money -> Roy acts quickly -> fright -> drops bag -> battered car -> easy to recognize -> police arrest。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 78.179,
      "end": 83.739,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是 Roy 的新工作。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Roy Trenton used to drive a taxi."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 84.089,
      "end": 96.032,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "used to drive"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示过去常做，但现在情况变了。他过去开 taxi；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A short while ago, however, he became a bus driver."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 96.382,
      "end": 102.606,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文接着说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he has not regretted it"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。意思是，他不后悔换工作。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 102.956,
      "end": 113.268,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么不后悔？"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He is finding his new work far more exciting."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "far more exciting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 much more exciting，刺激得多。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 113.618,
      "end": 126.378,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以第一幅画要像普通公交路线的开头：Roy 穿着公交司机制服，坐在 red city bus 里，街道平常，但问题已经埋下了：为什么公交会比出租车更 exciting？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 126.728,
      "end": 137.615,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，突然事件出现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When he was driving along Catford Street recently, he saw two thieves rush out of a shop and run towards a waiting car."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 137.965,
      "end": 147.769,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When he was driving"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一个 moving action。Roy 正在开车的时候，看见 another action：two thieves rush out。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 148.119,
      "end": 158.443,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rush out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是慢慢走出来，是突然、很快地冲出来。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "waiting car"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是已经准备好让他们逃走的车。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 158.793,
      "end": 164.841,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文还补了一条关键线索："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "One of them was carrying a bag full of money."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 165.19,
      "end": 177.35,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这幅画不要拍成 crime game。重点是 observation：shop, two thieves, tan money bag, green car, direction。看清线索，比冲上去更重要。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 177.7,
      "end": 184.588,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是动作和结果："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Roy acted quickly and drove the bus straight at the thieves."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 184.938,
      "end": 194.178,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里再提醒一次：Roy 是故事里的成人司机，不是现实里的儿童行动模板。现实中不要追，不要撞，不要靠近危险。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 194.528,
      "end": 201.168,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文最有画面感的一句来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The one with the money got such a fright that he dropped the bag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 201.518,
      "end": 210.766,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fright"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是突然的害怕。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "such a fright that he dropped the bag"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的感觉是：这一吓，吓得他包都掉了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 211.115,
      "end": 220.315,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句不是只背公式。镜头先给 sudden fright，再给 visible result：the bag drops。你一听就知道这个 fright 很强。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 220.665,
      "end": 234.177,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后 thieves 想逃："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As the thieves were trying to get away in their car, Roy drove his bus into the back of it."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "画面要控制，不要表现身体受伤，也不要把危险动作拍得很酷。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 234.527,
      "end": 244.015,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，重点从动作转到结果："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "While the battered car was moving away, Roy stopped his bus and telephoned the police."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 244.365,
      "end": 251.845,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "battered"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被撞坏、受损的。car 被 damaged 以后，就有了 very visible clue。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 252.195,
      "end": 261.742,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The thieves' car was badly damaged and easy to recognize."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是故事的关键：easy to recognize，容易辨认。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 262.092,
      "end": 268.104,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Shortly afterwards, the police stopped the car and both men were arrested."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 268.454,
      "end": 277.894,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结尾不是 Roy 继续追，而是 police stop the car。Roy 的快速行动让 car easy to recognize，警察随后把两个人都 arrested。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 278.244,
      "end": 280.724,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我们把这个故事的价值观说清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 281.074,
      "end": 284.688,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Roy 很勇敢，所以我们也应该追小偷吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 285.038,
      "end": 295.398,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不应该。这是 old action story 的写法。今天的安全选择是 keep distance, remember details, tell an adult, and call the police。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 295.747,
      "end": 300.241,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Stop thief!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么这么短？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 300.591,
      "end": 309.711,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它是 emergency shout，不是正式对话。像中文“捉贼！”一样，重点是让旁边的人知道发生了什么。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 310.061,
      "end": 315.957,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "such a fright that he dropped the bag"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么不用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "so frightened"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 316.306,
      "end": 328.578,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "so frightened"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更像描述他的状态：he was very frightened。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "got such a fright"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更像拍到那一下 shock，本身强到产生结果：he dropped the bag。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 328.928,
      "end": 337.966,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "when"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "as"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "while"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，它们都在讲同时发生的动作吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 338.316,
      "end": 350.916,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。Roy was driving, the thieves were trying to get away, the battered car was moving away。三个连接词让故事像视频一样，一边动，一边出现结果。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
