    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 475.911,
      "end": 484.031,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "battered"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么这个词重要？Because a battered car is easy to recognize. 车尾明显受损，警察就更容易辨认它。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 484.381,
      "end": 490.621,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 有两条线：moving actions，还有 strong cause -> visible result。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 490.971,
      "end": 501.171,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一条线是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "when"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "as"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "while"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它们让两个动作在同一段时间里发生。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 501.521,
      "end": 511.28,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When he was driving along Catford Street, he saw two thieves rush out."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Roy 正在开车；就在这段动作中，他看见小偷冲出来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 511.63,
      "end": 521.43,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As the thieves were trying to get away, Roy drove his bus into the back of it."
        },
        {
