      "end": 564.653,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天的语法板可以这样记：moving actions with when, as, while；strong shock with such a fright that；最后用 police result 收尾。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 70,
      "start": 565.003,
      "end": 572.203,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事里的 fast action 很 exciting。但现实里的 safe action 是 observe, remember, report。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 71,
      "start": 572.553,
      "end": 582.833,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现在把这课放进现代安全场景。你和大人在商店附近，看见两个人 suddenly rush out，朝一辆 car 跑去，其中一个 carrying a bag。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 72,
      "start": 583.183,
      "end": 592.903,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你的任务不是 chase them。你的安全选择是 move to a safe place，remember details，and tell an adult or call the police。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 73,
      "start": 593.253,
      "end": 601.493,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你要练三件事：say what you saw, give useful details, and say the safe action."
        }
      ]
    },
